---
title: Tender Stir-Fried Pork with Cashews and Black Bean Sauce
description: Black bean sauce is the foundation of many Chinese- Sichuan dishes. Its savoury and salty flavour adds an instant boost to quick stir-fries! Roasted cashews add a crunchy kick to this dish.
